{"lemma":"ذَرِيعِ","slug":"ذَرِيعِ","root":"ذ.ر.ع","root_slug":"ذ-ر-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ذ-ر-ع","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n13808","n13809","n13811"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B0%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B9%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"wide in step; rapid in pace"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"quick, abrupt, abject","tags":["figuratively"],"examples":[{"text":"لفت السياسي نديم الجابري اليوم الجمعة الى ان الخلافات واضحة في التحالف الشيعي ابرزها عملية تسجيل التحالفات لخوض الانتخابات المقبلة ، معتبرا انه لا توجد رؤية مشتركة لمكونات التحالف الوطني بشأن القضايا الوطنية والانشقاقات في الكتل السياسية ناتجة عن فشلها الذريع.","english":"The politician nadīm al-jābirī has on Friday drawn attention to the patent disagreements in the Shia alliance, most notably the alliances for the campaign for the election of the coming year, judging that there is no common vision about the constituents of the national alliance over the national affairs and the splits in the political blocs arising from their abject failure."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ða.riːʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n13808","headword_ar":"ذَرِيعٌ","root":"*rE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wide in step,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active, in pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) applied to a horse, (S, K,) and to a camel; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aruwEN","text_ar":"ذَرُوعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) [and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariEN","text_ar":"ذَرِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariEaAtN","text_ar":"ذَرِعَاتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) applied to the legs of a quadruped ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawaAy^imN","text_ar":"قَوَايِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), (S, TA,) signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wide in step, taking much of the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) or, as some say, this last word signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"legs"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a beast, (TA,) like ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma*aAriEu","text_ar":"مَذَارِعُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mi*oraAEN","text_ar":"مِذْرَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) It is said of Mohammad, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna","text_ar":"كَانَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariyEa Alma$oYi","text_ar":"ذَرِيعَ المَشْىِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was quick, and wide of step, in walking."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN *ariyEN biAlikitaAbapi","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ ذَرِيعٌ بِالِكِتَابَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man quick in writing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akala","text_ar":"اَكَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akolFA *ariyEFA","text_ar":"اَكْلًا ذَرِيعًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate quickly and much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatolN *ariyEN","text_ar":"قَتْلٌ ذَرِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quick slaughter."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawotN *ariyEN","text_ar":"مَوْتٌ ذَرِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Spreading death:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick, spreading death, such that the people can hardly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"can in no wise, bury one another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)  An"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ample"},{"kind":"text","text":"thing, affair, or state. (K.)       -A2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An intercessor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Msb","O","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n13809","headword_ar":"ذُرَيْعٌ","root":"*rE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iraAEN","text_ar":"ذِرَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n13811","headword_ar":"ذُرَيِّعٌ","root":"*rE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": dims. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iraAEN","text_ar":"ذِرَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}